        "TileImage": "$($repository 6b361407-9f8c-48d5-8169-2e9cabd9e3a5).Image",
        "Description": "47, an anonymous tip from a rival rebel force has revealed the real cuplrit behind the Morrocco scandal -masseuse Konny Engstrom. Your target has changed from Strandberg to Engstrom, along with his two spies. Zaydan remains a target.\r\rAdditionally, the client has requested all executions be carried out as exlosive accidents so the rebels can claim credit.\r\rFinally, to ensure we cannot be traced back to this operation, we request you complete the mission without firing a single shot.",
